title: Did OC say that the audience shouldn't see pictures of 11/9 because they were evasive?
subtitle: The attribution of questionable quotations to the U.S. Republic of Alexandria, Ocacio-Cortez, is a matter of concern to some people.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: The U.S. Republic of Alexandria Okasio Cortez said that the public should not see pictures of the 11/9 terrorist attacks on the U.S. because they are "free."
